nodes.text: A clone naval officer served aboard the Negotiator around 20 BBY.

While Commander Cody and Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi were discussing a rescue plan for Jedi Padawan Ahsoka Tano, who had been captured by Hondo Ohnaka and his gang and taken to Florrum, the clone naval officer reported to them that Separatist forces were approaching from hyperspace. This naval officer and many clone troopers were all killed by battle droids.
